FBIS4-2900 "drchi073_b_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 United States & Canada Qian Qichen Meets Canadian Doctor's Widow Qian Qichen Meets Canadian Doctor's Widow OW1504100694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0928 GMT 15 Apr 94 OW1504100694 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 15 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen met here this morning with Ella Endicott, widow of Dr. James Endicott, in the Diaoyutai State Guesthouse. Dr. Endicott, a renowned Canadian peace champion, is regarded as a life-long friend of the Chinese people. Dr. Endicott was born into a missionary family in Leshan city, in China's Sichuan Province, in December 1898, and died in Toronto, Canada, in November 1993.
